data.description: Must see! Stunning curb appeal & an outdoor sitting area at the entrance! Enter into a gorgeous foyer w/ art niche & beautiful lighting. Formal dining room to the left & generously sized. Continue forward & enter a huge living room open to the fabulous kitchen. Kitchen features custom cabinets, large island, granite, stainless steel appliances & an eat in breakfast nook. Master downstairs & huge! Master bath has double vanities, tiled shower & garden tub. Game room & media room upstairs w/ other bedrooms!
